dc_description_s: This data represents zoning in Lafayette County, Wisconsin in 2025 and includes the layers 'Lafayette_General_2025' and 'Lafayette_Shoreland_2025'. [Participating towns include: Argyle, Belmont, Elk Grove, Fayette, Gratiot, Kendall, Lamont, Monticello, Shullsburg, Wayne, & Wiota. Zoning Districts are as follows: A-1 Working Lands Initiative (Farmland Preservation Eligibility) A-2 Ag Lands RR Rural Residential R-1 Single Family Residential R-2 Multi Family Residential (Condo) R-3 Mobile Home Park or Multi Unit Residential B-1 Rural Business C-1 Commercial Business M-1 Light Industrial M-2 Heavy Industrial CFR Conservation, Forestry, and Recreation.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://lafay.maps.arcgis.com/apps/PublicGallery/index.html?appid=da8fbe9f3f7e4bf79d7178e007625930
